templateVersions.content:
 Assist the agent to respond to a customer in an ongoing customer service conversation provided below in the CONVERSATION TRANSCRIPT section.
 It must be for the agent to use in the next turn of the conversation.
 It must be concise and friendly.
 It must not repeat things the Agent has already said.
 The conversation context is provided below in the section CONVERSATION TRANSCRIPT.
 If the customer's words may be considered unethical and inappropriate, you must not repeat the inappropriate words in the response.
 Provide exactly two distinct answers.
 ###
 GROUNDING DATA:
 These are the grounding data relevant to the current conversation:
 {!$EinsteinSearch:KA_KB_Data_Library_1Cx_dPHb22b7600.results}
 ###
 CONVERSATION TRANSCRIPT:
 {!$Flow:conv_copilot_vc__GetTscpCall.Prompt}
###
RESPONSE:
You should provide an answer following the standard below:
{
"responses": [
{
"response": "<answer 1>",
"source": {
"sourceRecordId": "<sourceRecordId>",
"dataSourceObject": "<dataSourceObject>",
}
},
{
"response": "<answer 1>",
"source": {
"sourceRecordId": "<sourceRecordId>",
"dataSourceObject": "<dataSourceObject>",
}
}
]
}
